reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars SHARP, SAFE & STRONG IS THE BEAUTIFUL BLADE!
reviews.reviewText: I am extremely pleased with this purchase. The knives are presented in a burst of fun and attractive colors as shown in the photos. What is both wonderful, and thoughtful, are the durable protective covers designed for each knife. This is imperative as the blades are SHARP and cut decisively! So, do not allow small children to handle them. Also, don't let the economical price fool you. These blades are the boldest, brightest and baddest (most effective) in the box - and they're cute too! I almost hate to hide them away in my cutlery draw. They are so fine that they should be displayed. A HUGE value for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These are Great Daily Use Paring Knives
reviews.reviewText: These are sharp, good size for most paring, and the price is right. No reason to get those more expensive knives.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These paring knives are fantastic!
reviews.reviewText: I have used one of these paring knives so far and it was great! I used it to cut up a slab of ribs and it sliced smoothly through not only the meat but the bones, fat and cartilage as well. I didn't have to saw or hack or worry about slicing through my fingers if the knife slipped. One word of caution though. Even after cutting through all of those thick pork rib bones, the knife was still extremely sharp and I nicked my finger while cleaning the knife. Just by more careful than me.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The knives are quite sharp. The guards for the blades are appreciated. The blades are a bit flimsy, but for the price, I can’t expect Henkel.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I'm blown away at the sharpness of these paring knives at such an affordable price. Over decades of searching and buying others, I finally found the perfect paring knife. They're conveniently sheathed and has withstood several dishwasher cycles without rust spots. I'm buying another set to have on hand. I'd love the makers to create ones with wooden handles to use as steak knives because they're that sharp and perfectly sized.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I’m amazed at these knives. I have spent much more on paring knives but none were ever as sharp as these. Good that they come with a guard there that sharp. Best paring knives period. Don’t hesitate buy them.
